content.rendered:
Directed by Ksshitij Chaudhary

Written by Amberdeep Singh

Star Gurnam Bhullar(Raja). Sargun Mehta(Roopi). Mintu Kapa(Sukha). Jass Bajwa(Jassa). Jasmin Bajwa(Saanjh). Hardeep Gill(Master Baldev Singh). Parminder Gill(Roopi’s mother). Ram Aujla(Nachhattar Singh). Shivika Diwan(Deepi). Baljinder Kaur(Tailor). Suvinder Vicky(Saanjh’s father). Deep Mandeep(Deepi’s mother). Mohini Toor(Saanjh’s mother). Satinder Kaur Dhiman(Raja’s mother (as Satwinder Kaur)). Labh Chatamliwala(Village Oldman). Sukhi Patiala(Bhaanimaar gawaandhan). Sameep Ranaut(Laadi). Ramandeep Jagga(Ielts girl). Guri Billing(Ashiq in bus). Riar Parm(Roopi’s village girl). Anmol Kaur. Mandy Brar. Renu Mohali. Ravinder Sawhney. Channpreet Gill

Language Punjabi

Producers Apoorv Ghai. Sarab Gill. Varun Jhamb. Vaneet Kumar. Vicky Makhu. Navdeep Narula. Gabbar Sangrur. Jitendra Sharma. Gurjit Singh. Gurjit Singh. Kamaljit Singh. Mansi Singh. Yuvraj S Singh. Mandeep Singh Taunque. Ankit Vijan. Kiran Yadav

Production New Era Films. Shri narotam ji films
